We are looking for an ambitious and energetic Marketing Executive / Senior Marketing Executive to join our sales team. The ideal candidate should be a creative & analytical thinker, willing to work as a team member and pay attention to details.


Job Responsibilities:

Explore new business opportunities and various ways to reach target customers like listed companies, financial & professional firms;
Work closely with different internal and external business units to develop a client service strategy, execute a range of insightful and creative campaigns that support clients' business programs;
Project management duties including but not limited to coordinating/ participating in various activities of quotation preparation, typesetting, proof-reading, design, artwork and printing production under tight deadlines;        
Develop and maintain good relationship with potential and existing clients; and
Brand building and promotion.
Job Requirements:

Bachelor's degree in Business, Marketing or related discipline;
2 years or above experience gained at marketing, PR, media or advertising agencies and/or financial printing house is preferred;
As an effective communicator, able to synthesize complex and diverse material into information that can engage our target customers;
Experience in servicing corporate clients & developing strategic business plans is an advantage;
Energetic, well-organized and capable of keeping a positive attitude;
Good command of spoken English and Mandarin and written English and Chinese;
Fresh graduate will also be considered; and
Candidate with more experience will be considered as Senior Marketing Executive.

We offer competitive remuneration package. Interested parties please send full resume including date of availability, current and expected salary to HR Department, 2/F, 100QRC, 100 Queen’s Road Central, Hong Kong or by fax to 2523 7232 or by clicking apply now.

